      "fix": "Migrated navbar.tsx to Base UI idioms: replaced every `asChild` with the `render={<a/>}` / `render={<Button/>}` prop, changed Accordion to `openMultiple={false}`, and removed `viewport={false}` from NavigationMenu.",
